        <mxCell id="qPgVKRsB_RX_aEyV6NZG-31" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Idea&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Server-side chunkloading service.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every player on the server should be able to load/unload chunks. Which chunks are loaded/unloaded should be stored on disk so it&#39;s persistent across server restarts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Future&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;Server API with running webserver using something like Python&#39;s fastAPI. Data about the server and which chunks are loaded can then be displayed on a webpage, running on the same server.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
